<p id="fs-id1165042444934">Find the local linear approximation to <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mroot><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></mroot></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mroot><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></mroot></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> at <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> Use it to approximate <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mroot><mrow><mn>8.1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mroot></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mroot><mrow><mn>8.1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mroot></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> to five decimal places.</p>
</div>
